<Routes>
  <Route path="/" element={<Home />} />
  {/* ... other routes */}
  <Route path="/Skills/*" element={<Skills />} />
          <Route path="/Services/*" element={<Services />} />
		  <Route path="/ResumeAndCertificates/*" element={<ResumeAndCertificates />} />
          <Route path="/AboutMe/*" element={<AboutMe />} />
  <Route
    path="/casual/*"
    element={
      <AppWithNavbar navbar={<NavbarCasual />} isCasual={true} isProfessional={false}>
        <Portfolio isCasual={true} isProfessional={false} />
      </AppWithNavbar>
    }
  />
  <Route
    path="/professional/*"
    element={
      <AppWithNavbar navbar={<NavbarProfessional />} isCasual={false} isProfessional={true}>
        <Portfolio isCasual={false} isProfessional={true} />
      </AppWithNavbar>
    }
  />
  <Route
    path="/Portfolio/*"
    element={
      <AppWithNavbar navbar={<NavbarCasual />} isCasual={true} isProfessional={false}>
        <Portfolio isCasual={true} isProfessional={false} />
      </AppWithNavbar>
    }
  />
  <Route
    path="/casual/*"
    element={
      <AppWithNavbar navbar={<NavbarCasual />} isCasual={true} isProfessional={false}>
        <Contact isCasual={true} isProfessional={false} />
      </AppWithNavbar>
    }
  />
  <Route
    path="/professional/*"
    element={
      <AppWithNavbar navbar={<NavbarProfessional />} isCasual={false} isProfessional={true}>
        <Contact isCasual={false} isProfessional={true} />
      </AppWithNavbar>
    }
  />
  <Route
    path="/Contact/*"
    element={
      <AppWithNavbar navbar={<NavbarCasual />} isCasual={true} isProfessional={false}>
        <Contact isCasual={true} isProfessional={false} />
      </AppWithNavbar>
    }
  />
  {/* ... other routes */}
  <Route path="/Skills/*" element={<Skills />} />
          <Route path="/Services/*" element={<Services />} />
		  <Route path="/ResumeAndCertificates/*" element={<ResumeAndCertificates />} />
          <Route path="/AboutMe/*" element={<AboutMe />} />
</Routes>
